rdf:Description.Label: What data objects do systems create and how many other systems create that same data?

rdf:Description.SPARQL: SELECT (SAMPLE(?system1) AS ?sys1) (SAMPLE(?data) AS ?Data) (SAMPLE(COALESCE(?system2, '')) AS ?examplesys) (COALESCE(COUNT(DISTINCT(?system2)), 0) AS ?totalSys) WHERE { {?system1 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/ActiveSystem>;} {?provide <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Provide>;} {?provide <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/CRM> 'C'} {?data <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/DataObject> ;} {?system1 ?provide ?data ;} OPTIONAL { {?system2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/ActiveSystem>;} {?provide2 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Provide>;} {?provide2 <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/CRM> 'C'}{?system2 ?provide2 ?data .} FILTER (?system1 != ?system2) } BIND(URI(CONCAT(STR(?system1),STR(?data))) AS ?sysData)} GROUP BY ?sysData

rdf:Description.Label: What BLU do systems create and how many other systems create that same BLU?

rdf:Description.SPARQL: SELECT (SAMPLE(?system1) AS ?sys1) (SAMPLE(?blu) AS ?BLU) (SAMPLE(COALESCE(?system2, '')) AS ?examplesys) (COALESCE(COUNT(DISTINCT(?system2)), 0) AS ?totalSys) WHERE { {?system1 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/ActiveSystem>;} {?provide <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Provide>;} {?blu <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/BusinessLogicUnit> ;} {?system1 ?provide ?blu ;} OPTIONAL { {?system2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/ActiveSystem>;} {?provide2 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Provide>;} {?system2 ?provide2 ?blu .} FILTER (?system1 != ?system2) } BIND(URI(CONCAT(STR(?system1),STR(?blu))) AS ?sysBLU)} GROUP BY ?sysBLU

rdf:Description.SPARQL: SELECT DISTINCT ?SoftwareVersion (COALESCE(xsd:dateTime(?SoftMlifePot), COALESCE(xsd:dateTime(?EOLPotential),'TBD')) AS ?EOL) (COALESCE(?SoftwareVersionUpgradePotential, '') AS ?SoftwareVersionUpgrade) (COALESCE(?QuantityModule,?QuantityVer) AS ?Quantity) (COALESCE(?CostPotential, 0.0) AS ?Cost) WHERE { BIND(<@System-http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/ActiveSystem@> AS ?System){?Has <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Consists>;}{?SoftwareModule <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/SoftwareModule>;}{?TypeOf <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/TypeOf>;}{?System ?Has ?SoftwareModule} {?SoftwareModule ?TypeOf ?SoftwareVersion }{?SoftwareVersion <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/SoftwareVersion>;} OPTIONAL {?SoftwareModule <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/Quantity> ?QuantityModule ;}OPTIONAL {?SoftwareVersion <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/Quantity> ?QuantityVersion ;}OPTIONAL{?SoftwareModule <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/EOL> ?SoftMlifePot ;}OPTIONAL{?SoftwareVersion <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/EOL> ?EOLPotential ;}OPTIONAL{{?Phase <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Upgrade>;}{?SoftwareVersionUpgradePotential <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/SoftwareVersion>;} {?SoftwareVersion ?Phase ?SoftwareVersionUpgradePotential.}}OPTIONAL{?SoftwareVersion <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/Price> ?CostPotential ;}BIND(IF(!BOUND(?QuantityVersion),0,?QuantityVersion) AS ?QuantityVer)}

rdf:Description.Label: What is the hardware life cycle for a specific system?

rdf:Description.SPARQL: SELECT DISTINCT ?HardwareVersion (COALESCE(xsd:dateTime(?HardMlifePot), COALESCE(xsd:dateTime(?EOLPotential),'TBD')) AS ?EOL) (COALESCE(?HardwareVersionUpgradePotential, '') AS ?HardwareVersionUpgrade) (COALESCE(?QuantityModule,?QuantityVer) AS ?Quantity) (COALESCE(?CostPotential, 0.0) AS ?Cost) WHERE { BIND(<@System-http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/ActiveSystem@> AS ?System){?Has <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Has>;}{?HardwareModule <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/HardwareModule>;}{?TypeOf <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/TypeOf>;}{?System ?Has ?HardwareModule} {?HardwareModule ?TypeOf ?HardwareVersion }{?HardwareVersion <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/HardwareVersion>;} OPTIONAL {?HardwareModule <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/Quantity> ?QuantityModule ;}OPTIONAL {?HardwareVersion <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/Quantity> ?QuantityVersion ;}OPTIONAL{?HardwareModule <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/EOL> ?HardMlifePot ;}OPTIONAL{?HardwareVersion <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/EOL> ?EOLPotential ;}OPTIONAL{{?Phase <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Upgrade>;}{?HardwareVersionUpgradePotential <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Concept/HardwareVersion>;} {?HardwareVersion ?Phase ?HardwareVersionUpgradePotential.}}OPTIONAL{?HardwareVersion <http://semoss.org/ontologies/Relation/Contains/Price> ?CostPotential ;}BIND(IF(!BOUND(?QuantityVersion),0,?QuantityVersion) AS ?QuantityVer)}
